description: ELECTRONIC DISCOVERY AGREEMENT AND ORDER: This Agreement and Order will govern how the parties manage electronic discovery in the above-captioned case. Specifically, the parties will attempt in good faith to come to an agreement on search and culling methods used to identify responsive information.
